Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Thomas Paine and the uprisings in Czechoslovakia and Hungary
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydt58
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 1 Dec 1989
A profile of American revolutionary Thomas Paine, the rebellions in Czechoslovakia and Hungary, and President Bush's reluctance to comment on the uprisings.